Super simple and incredible spicy pasta served on a bed of tofu lemon garlic herb whipped ricotta! Recipe at rabbitandwolves.com/vegan-spicy-tomato-basil-shells or click the link in my profile @rabbitandwolves 
Side note: the tiny hands making the ricotta belong to my daughter. She wanted credit for her work😄
